bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.feature

Class FeatureLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.feature.FeatureLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class FeatureLocation
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A FeatureLocation is used to describe a feature position that cannot be represented using a single pair of from and to values. This class is intended to handle locations as described in the official NCBI/EBI/DDBJ Feature Table specification document.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
    See Also:
